<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6477721>
    dc:description "fig. 6) of Eryma fossata (Oxfordian, Galgenberg near Hildesheim, Germany); J, original figure of Sauvage (1891: pl. 4, fig. 6) of Eryma leblanci (Kimmeridgian, Boulogne-sur-Mer, France); K, original figure of Sauvage (1891: pl. 3, fig. 5) of Eryma boloniensis (Kimmeridgian, Boulogne-sur-Mer, France); L, original figure of Sauvage (1891: pl. 4, fig. 3) of Eryma beaugrandi (Kimmeridgian,Boulogne-sur-Mer,France); M, N, original figures of Morière (1883: pl. 1, figs 1-2) of the syntypes of Eryma villersi (Oxfordian, Villers-sur-Mer, France); O, original figure of Van Straelen (1925: pl. 9, fig. 1) of the holotype of Eryma morieri Hée, 1924 (Oxfordian, Villers-sur-Mer, France); P, Q, specimen from the Callovian of Villers-sur-Mer (France, private collection of J.-P. Pezy). Photographs: L. Cazes. Scale bars: 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6477721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

